channel.title: Help with Character Titles
channel.description: So I dumped the TrisidiaX V3 RSPS (I won't be working on that.. because of an annoying tree.) and I got Acheron V1 and I'm absolutely digging it. But the creator of this source/client made a typo. He made a bunch of new ranks and crowns and titles. Well, I have access to the crowns, and ranks, but I can't seem to find the titles. I've done a search for 'title', 'character-t', and 'character-title'. In the .txt file for MY character, Dax.txt, there is Character-title = 7 which in the game says "Developper Dax" any help on this? I wpuld like to edit some titles.

item.title: Help with Character Titles
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:

The titles are in your client. Search for one of the titles in the Client.java of your client.
